job_description: We are looking for an experienced Frontend Developer to join our team. You will be responsible for building user-facing web applications using React, TypeScript, and modern web technologies. Strong experience with Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and state management libraries is required.
Join our backend team to build scalable APIs and microservices. We work with Node.js, Python, PostgreSQL, and AWS. Experience with Docker, Kubernetes, and CI/CD pipelines is a plus.

We're seeking a talented Full Stack Developer to work on exciting fintech projects. You'll work with React, Node.js, MongoDB, and cloud technologies. Remote work available with occasional office visits in London.
Contract position for 6 months with possibility of extension. Work on a cutting-edge e-commerce platform using React, Redux, and GraphQL. Must have 3+ years of React experience.
Join our team developing enterprise software solutions. We use Java, Spring Boot, Angular, and PostgreSQL. German language skills are preferred but not required. Great benefits and work-life balance.
Perfect opportunity for a junior developer to grow their skills. Work with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and learn React on the job. Flexible hours and mentorship provided.
Lead our DevOps initiatives using AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, and Terraform. Experience with CI/CD pipelines and infrastructure as code is essential. Competitive salary and equity options.
Develop mobile applications for iOS and Android using React Native. Experience with native development (Swift/Kotlin) is a plus. Work on apps used by millions of users across Asia.
Freelance opportunity to build custom WordPress themes and plugins. Must have strong PHP, JavaScript, and CSS skills. Remote work with flexible hours.
Work on AI and machine learning projects using Python, TensorFlow, and Django. Experience with data science libraries like pandas and numpy is preferred. Innovative projects and great team culture.
